Our Batman vs Azrael 2 pack from Batman: Curse of the White Knight is available for pre-order NOW at select retailers and more to follow!⁠
Link in bio ⬆️⁠ ⁠
⁠
These 7” figures include a Batarang with rope, two rapiers with sheath, Azrael’s sword, two collectible art cards and a flaming display base for posing.⁠

Azrael is the Dark Knight's most powerful new threat, and the one living link to a devastating secret about the Wayne family's legacy in Gotham City. In an effort to overthrow Batman, Azrael dons an armored Bat suit of his own and threatens to take control of the city. It’s up to Batman to stop the super-villain before the secret is revealed. ⁠
⁠
#DCMultiverse #McFarlaneToys
